Package: AutoRef
Title: Automatically Searching Literature from the PubMed Database
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Na", "Luo", email = "naluo.luona@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package enhances the functionality of the 'rentrez' package, offering 
    a more user-friendly approach to searching and exporting literature from the PubMed 
    database. It supports the automatic generation of .ris files for use with citation 
    management software such as Zotero and EndNote. Additionally, it provides functionality 
    to visualize the distribution of publications over time in a graphical format (.tiff).
